interestingcomments.content: How to get rid of spots on photos? /!/ A lot of my photos are coming out with what appears to be dust or spots on the pictures. [Here](https://imgur.com/q3yfAEp) is an example.  I have a Canon EOS T5 and I primarily use an EFS 10-18mm for landscape and weather photos. I have tried cleaning the mirror and the sensor and the spots still remain. Any ideas of how to fix this issues?
